==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Kurd
<hw>Kurd</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>A member of a
people who inhabit a mountainous region of Western Asia, sometimes
referred to as Kurdistan, spread over an area including adjoining parts
of Turkey, Iran, Iraq, Armenia, Azerbaijan, and Syria. The people of
this region speak Kurdish and are mostly Moslem.</def> <altsp>[Written
also <asp>Koord</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Kurdish</ent>⟦br⟧
